{
  "stem": "5761.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I can say proudly that this was the decisive battle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In other words, we didn't have tens of thousands of soldiers, very hard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We must have lost 60%, killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But then we got reinforcement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we succeeded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In 1992 was a reunion in Israel about Hativat Givati [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and the Negev, being there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A man jumped on me, crying, and hugging me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he said, Dov, I don't believe it's you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He says, for the last forty years, I was thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I know you were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was quite a moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But, anyway, then we were transferred to another camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I would say for about three weeks, we used to go out every night to a battle to attack.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And normally, under normal circumstances, soldiers allowed to go out to a battle every third day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "One day, he goes to a battle, two days, he rests.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We used to go every, every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We used to lose a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my main fronts were the Negev.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I believe I was a pretty good commander.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And soldiers used to fight to be in my unit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I-- see normally, the officers are in back of the unit attacking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always used to be always the first one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of the decisive battles was Hill 105.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hill 105, there were, if you-- you know where Negba is?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Negba was surrounded with hill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Negba was taken over once by Egyptian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then they were retreated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came back from an action.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
